`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`The `}<em parentName="p">{`setName`}</em>{` is the strongly typed function of the action that you use to dispatch later on. It is linked to the specific string literal ACTION_SET_NAME (unique identifier) and the payload that can be passed to the action is only a string. You invoke the action by calling that function with the payload that you desire:`}</p>
